/resource/Senate_of_the_Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9998445423778918, \"rank\": 0.00015518543450299683, \"text\": \"Senate President\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Senate_of_the_Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Senate_of_the_Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 4603, \"end\": 4609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barksdale_Organization\", \"score\": 0.9999998239418502, \"rank\": 1.7493556116874447e-07, \"text\": \"Gerard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barksdale_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barksdale_Organization\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"now a member\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4491}, {\"ngram\": \"parliament\", \"from\": 4495, \"to\": 4505}, {\"ngram\": \"center\", \"from\": 4520, \"to\": 4526}, {\"ngram\": \"the names\", \"from\": 4627, \"to\": 4636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As none of those men are likely to secure a majority in the new parliament, their government would remain in caretaker register for a few weeks.\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 4652, \"to\": 4656}, {\"ngram\": \"those men\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4669}, {\"ngram\": \"a majority\", \"from\": 4691, \"to\": 4701}, {\"ngram\": \"the new parliament\", \"from\": 4705, \"to\": 4723}, {\"ngram\": \"their government\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4741}, {\"ngram\": \"caretaker register\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4776}, {\"ngram\": \"a few weeks\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next move could be naming a candidate from the leftist coalition known as the New Popular Font (NPF).\", \"from\": 4795, \"to\": 4900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4895, \"end\": 4898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.771392419663406e-15, \"text\": \"NPF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The next move\", \"from\": 4795, \"to\": 4808}, {\"ngram\": \"a candidate\", \"from\": 4825, \"to\": 4836}, {\"ngram\": \"the leftist coalition\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4863}, {\"ngram\": \"the New Popular Font\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At present that candidate is Lucie Castets, a little-known functionary but a consensus figure in the deeply divided group.\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 5023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4936, \"end\": 4943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\", \"score\": 0.5009607382045541, \"rank\": 0.6944444444443503, \"text\": \"Castets\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Castets_(grape)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that candidate\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4926}, {\"ngram\": \"a little-known functionary\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 4971}, {\"ngram\": \"a consensus figure\", \"from\": 4976, \"to\": 4994}, {\"ngram\": \"the deeply divided group\", \"from\": 4998, \"to\": 5022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the NPF, though it has the largest number of members in the new parliament is far short of a simple majority.\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5033, \"end\": 5036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.771392419663406e-15, \"text\": \"NPF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the largest number\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5070}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 5074, \"to\": 5081}, {\"ngram\": \"the new parliament\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5103}, {\"ngram\": \"a simple majority\", \"from\": 5120, \"to\": 5137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thus, Premier-designate Castets, too, would have to throw in the towel after a few weeks.\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Premier-designate Castets\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5170}, {\"ngram\": \"the towel\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5209}, {\"ngram\": \"a few weeks\", \"from\": 5216, \"to\": 5227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Naming someone from the National Rally (RN), the ultra-right which Macron has often cast as the devil seems unlikely but not impossible.\", \"from\": 5230, \"to\": 5366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5297, \"end\": 5303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.258899208786371e-27, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 5237, \"to\": 5244}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Rally\", \"from\": 5250, \"to\": 5268}, {\"ngram\": \"RN\", \"from\": 5270, \"to\": 5272}, {\"ngram\": \"the ultra-\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5285}, {\"ngram\": \"the devil\", \"from\": 5322, \"to\": 5331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, RN, which has the third largest number of seats in the parliament, will also be unlikely to find a majority.\", \"from\": 5367, \"to\": 5484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5376, \"end\": 5378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\", \"score\": 0.595499458463197, \"rank\": 0.6792618037983887, \"text\": \"RN\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Rally\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third largest number\", \"from\": 5390, \"to\": 5414}, {\"ngram\": \"seats\", \"from\": 5418, \"to\": 5423}, {\"ngram\": \"the parliament\", \"from\": 5427, \"to\": 5441}, {\"ngram\": \"a majority\", \"from\": 5473, \"to\": 5483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its PM-designate would thus join other marionettes that make three rounds and fall down.\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its PM-designate\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5501}, {\"ngram\": \"other marionettes\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5535}, {\"ngram\": \"three rounds\", \"from\": 5546, \"to\": 5558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, even if Macron turns out to be a master puppeteer whom I doubt he is the Machiavellian scenario explained above might not be easy to stage for months on end.\", \"from\": 5575, \"to\": 5741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5592, \"end\": 5598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.258899208786371e-27, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 5657, \"end\": 5670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Machiavellian_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.514891290784739e-21, \"text\": \"Machiavellian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Machiavellian_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Machiavellian_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a master puppeteer\", \"from\": 5615, \"to\": 5633}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 5727, \"to\": 5733}, {\"ngram\": \"end\", \"from\": 5737, \"to\": 5740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The least risky way out of the current maze is for Macron to allow his parliamentary group to vote for a NPF candidate but refuse to vote for the leftist bloc's silliest pseudo-Maoist program.\", \"from\": 5743, \"to\": 5935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5794, \"end\": 5800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.258899208786371e-27, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 5848, \"end\": 5851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.771392419663406e-15, \"text\": \"NPF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Police_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the current maze\", \"from\": 5770, \"to\": 5786}, {\"ngram\": \"his parliamentary group\", \"from\": 5810, \"to\": 5833}, {\"ngram\": \"the leftist bloc's silliest pseudo-Maoist program\", \"from\": 5885, \"to\": 5934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That would provide time and space for the least ideologically-afflicted members of the bloc, some of them with a culture of governance to remember that politics is the art of the possible not Aladdin's magic lamp.\", \"from\": 5936, \"to\": 6149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6128, \"end\": 6135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aladdin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1616372813554644e-16, \"text\": \"Aladdin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aladdin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aladdin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 5959}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 5964, \"to\": 5969}, {\"ngram\": \"the least ideologically-afflicted members\", \"from\": 5974, \"to\": 6015}, {\"ngram\": \"the bloc\", \"from\": 6019, \"to\": 6027}, {\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 6047, \"to\": 6056}, {\"ngram\": \"governance\", \"from\": 6060, \"to\": 6070}, {\"ngram\": \"politics\", \"from\": 6088, \"to\": 6096}, {\"ngram\": \"the art\", \"from\": 6100, \"to\": 6107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back to Olympics, will Los-Angeles match the magnificence that Paris offered?\", \"from\": 6151, \"to\": 6228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6174, \"end\": 6185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los-Angeles\",